<plot>A plastic covered sofa is the most important thing for this middle class latinamerican housewife. Being a devout evangelical christian, she drives away her husband, who the night before their son's birthday isn't afraid to show everybody one of his social experiments. The son is in the middle, glimpsing at life through a hole on a piece of paper, sitting in the plastic covered sofa that in the end will cover a tragedy.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?173807</url></doc>
